column5: I'll be celebratin' Dawg's Birthday, by headin' fer the fridge!
Weeee doggies!!! I'm a celebratin' too!... done made 2 trips to the root cellar!  I wonder if'n Elly Mae wants to wrassle?
Happy barf day to you.... happy barf day to you....   G
I think yer purdier than a Speckled Bass Elly!!!
Thats a good way to arouse the Dawg
Happy birthday, hope Granny, Jethro and Elly good to ya!  Have a sip o' rheumatis medicine and a dip in the ceement pond.
I can hear him a howlin' all the way from Allibamy
